! ProseMirror 编辑器设置

这些设置控制ProseMirror编辑器的行为。

!! 基本设置

|<<lingo Settings/Heading>>|
|自动保存 |<$select tiddler="$:/plugins/oeyoews/tiddlywiki-prosemirror/config/autoSave" default="yes">
<option value="yes">是</option>
<option value="no">否</option>
</$select> |
|启用历史记录 |<$select tiddler="$:/plugins/oeyoews/tiddlywiki-prosemirror/config/historyEnabled" default="yes">
<option value="yes">是</option>
<option value="no">否</option>
</$select> |
|启用拖放光标 |<$select tiddler="$:/plugins/oeyoews/tiddlywiki-prosemirror/config/dropCursorEnabled" default="yes">
<option value="yes">是</option>
<option value="no">否</option>
</$select> |
|启用间隙光标 |<$select tiddler="$:/plugins/oeyoews/tiddlywiki-prosemirror/config/gapCursorEnabled" default="yes">
<option value="yes">是</option>
<option value="no">否</option>
</$select> |

!! Markdown 设置

|<<lingo Settings/Heading>>|
|启用Markdown支持 |<$select tiddler="$:/plugins/oeyoews/tiddlywiki-prosemirror/config/markdownEnabled" default="yes">
<option value="yes">是</option>
<option value="no">否</option>
</$select> |
|自动检测Markdown |<$select tiddler="$:/plugins/oeyoews/tiddlywiki-prosemirror/config/autoDetectMarkdown" default="yes">
<option value="yes">是</option>
<option value="no">否</option>
</$select> |
|强制使用Markdown |<$select tiddler="$:/plugins/oeyoews/tiddlywiki-prosemirror/config/forceMarkdown" default="no">
<option value="yes">是</option>
<option value="no">否</option>
</$select> |

